# TERMS AND CONDITIONS

Last Updated: May 15, 2025

## 1. Acceptance of Terms

By adding HoYo Code Sender Discord Bot ("the bot") to your server or using any of its features, you agree to these Terms and Conditions and our Privacy Policy. If you do not agree with these terms, please do not use the bot.

## 2. Description of Service

HoYo Code Sender Discord Bot is a service that automatically fetches and sends redemption codes for HoYoverse games (Genshin Impact, Honkai: Star Rail, and Zenless Zone Zero) to designated Discord channels.

**IMPORTANT NOTICE:** This bot is NOT affiliated with, endorsed by, or connected to HoYoverse (miHoYo) in any way. This is a fan-made tool created to help the community. All game names, logos, and related content are trademarks and copyrights of HoYoverse (miHoYo).

## 3. User Obligations

As a user of the bot, you agree to:
- Use the bot in compliance with Discord's Terms of Service
- Not use the bot to distribute harmful, offensive, or illegal content
- Not attempt to exploit, reverse engineer, or manipulate the bot's functionality
- Not use the bot for spam, harassment, or any abusive behavior

## 4. Limitations and Availability

- The bot retrieves codes from third-party sources and does not guarantee the accuracy, validity, or timeliness of redemption codes
- Service availability may be subject to downtime for maintenance, updates, or technical issues
- Features may change, be added, or removed at any time without prior notice

## 5. Data Collection

Please refer to our [Privacy Policy](https://github.com/chiraitori/HoYo_Code_Sender_Discord_Bot/blob/main/PRIVACY.md) for details about what data we collect and how we use it.

